// Unity Class: QualitySettings
// Documentation: https://docs.unity3d.com/ScriptReference/QualitySettings.html

// Description: This represents the script interface for Quality Settings.

// Properties:
// - hideFlags: Should the object be hidden, saved with the Scene or modifiable by the user?
// - name: The name of the object.

